Package au.edu.anu.omhtk.preferences

Interface Preferenceable

public interface Preferenceable
Interface for the preferences system. It is intended that implementations of this interface provide a means of saving arrays. Maybe there's a better way?
Author:
Ian Davies - Dec 11, 2018
